videos.headline: Lawrence thinks Clemson is best team in country
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence says Clemson is ready for the College Football Playoff and to prove the Tigers are the best team the country.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Lawrence thinks Clemson is best team in country) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Higgins, Lawrence fuel Clemson to rout and fifth straight ACC title
videos.description: Virginia has no answers for Tee Higgins who goes off for 182 yards and three touchdowns in Clemson's 62-17 win. Trevor Lawrence finishes with four TDs and 302 yards in the win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Higgins, Lawrence fuel Clemson to rout and 5th-straight ACC title) 2019/12/07 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Swinney, Clemson back up the talk in conference championship
videos.description: Head coach Dabo Swinney and the Clemson Tigers top UVa in a statement win to lock up their 5th straight ACC Championship.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Clemson Backs Up Talk) 2019/12/08 ESHEET SOTFULL
